value.0: Hey, Traveller. Wanna help us with a Tusken problem?
Kill enough of em, and i'll sort you out with some wicked walls.
Fifty to start with. Then we'll go from there.
Already sorted em' out?
Already sorted em' out?
We've just got reports that more are out there, and they're going after moisture farms. Feel like going again?
That was quick. All done?
That was quick. All done?
Great work, saves us having to le-... I mean, allows us to guard Anchorhead... More of them are going after trade routes. Got another Fifty in ya?
And you're back... Sort em out?
And you're back... Sort em out?
Well... Anchorhead thanks you for your service... You know, i've been thinking... Why not just go to their camp and take out Five Hundred of them?
We'd do it ourselves, but, ya know... Boss is watching us and we can't go to far... You'd be doing us a huge service.
Surely you haven't killed Five Hundred?
Surely you haven't killed Five Hundred?
Woah woah... Lower your voice... No reason to cause a scene... Take this and go... Jeez.
What? You want something more? I paid ya and gave you those cool schematics... Now... Move along.
Hey... Thanks again for your help... If we get any more jobs, i'll keep you in mind.
Nah, i'm good thanks.
Sure. What's in it for me?
Sure, how many are we talking?
Right. I'll be back shortly.
Nope. Been busy.
Yeah, all done.
I think Fifty was enough... I'm done.
Another Fifty then? Sure, I can handle that.
No... It's a lot of Byysk.
Yup, One Hundred total.
Are you serious? No, go do it yourself.
... Sure, I've got nothing better to do.
Not yet...
Yup... But, no signs of any trade routes being taken...
You've got to be joking...
You have got to be joking. No. I am done.
... Fine. But this better be worth my time.
No, i'm still working on it.
No, not at all... I was out there, in the hot sand, and I got to thinking... Why am I out here, while he's in there... Standing around, doing nothing!
Whatever.
Please don't...
